            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>使者啊！“我”确已赐福你很多的福利，其中就包括乐园中的多福之河。</p>"
        },
        "2": {
            "verses": {
                "108:2": {
                    "id": 2
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>为了感谢真主给予的恩惠，你应只为祂礼拜和宰献牲，这有别于以物配主者为了接近他们的偶像而为其宰献牲。</p>"
        },
        "3": {
            "verses": {
                "108:3": {
                    "id": 3
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>的确，怨恨你者确是远离一切福利的。凡以任何不良语言提到你的，都归于怨恨你者。</p>"
        }
    }
}